{"tid":2260194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"年售500屋 本研社：套丁深入骨髓","createTime":"2020-10-27T11:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T12:04:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72852bde7f04e6f2de38cf5e6985dd9e799d7337","tid":2260194,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/6KBWZD3OQZHNFFAI3O4QNM5H2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F6KBWZD3OQZHNFFAI3O4QNM5H2Y%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=74c5d32d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F6KBWZD3OQZHNFFAI3O4QNM5H2Y%2F&h=83a4238f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/6KBWZD3OQZHNFFAI3O4QNM5H2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n年售500屋 本研社：套丁深入骨髓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LpYCI2_Q7TUTHM_4-WR5MeDYKqs=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YZJDGNT22FHTTLQTH3JKMZHFEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLpYCI2_Q7TUTHM_4-WR5MeDYKqs%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYZJDGNT22FHTTLQTH3JKMZHFEE.jpg&h=116ab6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■本土研究社昨發表新界套丁報告，批評政府默許亂象發生。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】新界丁屋規劃雜亂無章，民間團體本土研究社昨發表新一份新界「套丁」報告，顯示過去五年獲准轉售的丁屋每年維持約300至500宗，未見明顯下跌。由於申請轉售是套丁必經步驟，數據反映套丁問題沒改善。本研社成員陳劍青形容套丁行為已「深入骨髓」，「早幾年喺林鄭治下，幾乎平均每日一宗（疑似套丁個案）。成個新界套丁潛在利益已散播晒，尤其係元朗區」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地政僅叫申請人「自首」<br />\n<br />\n本研社成員黃肇鴻指，以前以為套丁問題只涉鄉黑，。。。。。。。。。，「一有套丁迹象，政府大可以卡住佢」。<br />\n<br />\n對於地政總署聲言自去年底已主動向丁屋申請人提問有否涉及套丁，。。。。。。。。。。。。他認為當局必須加強把關和徹查丁屋申請。<br />\n<br />\n本研社套丁報告抽查發現，。。。。。。。。。。。。，「𠵱家唔係真丁定假丁，而係可以拎個真嘅丁權去進行（懷疑）違規嘅發展，違反丁屋政策原意係自住」。<br />\n<br />\n陳劍青指報告發佈前，。。。。。。。。。。。，「你嘅職員如果有outside practice，公司應該要清楚」。"},{"pid":"e199fd98a0e78c0949eb3fa00b2c692c6e692063","tid":2260194,"uid":78440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1a2eb442287da01873ac01685cfaa2c6ffe3a3","tid":2260194,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"套丁是狗"},{"pid":"cb4e6c5ac973194251cd15f9fa5057d90d8648bf","tid":2260194,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:04:55.000Z","msg":"正仆街"}]}